data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description:
U.S. Marines with 2nd Battalion, 4th Marine Regiment, participate in a Fire Support Coordination Exercise(FSCEX) together with the Australian Regular Army at Mount Bundey Training Area, Northern Territory, Australia, Aug. 11, 2018. FSCEX was the culmination multilateral fire-support event for Marine Rotational Force Darwin 18.

(U.S. Marine Corps video by Sgt. Antonio Campbell. Additional video footage by Staff Sgt. Daniel Wetzel)
